README - Dogvibes 0.X
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation notes:
1. Update dogvibes.conf to suit your target system (user="username"),
   copy the file to "/etc/dbus-1/system.d/dogvibes.conf" and restart
   dbus-daemon
2. Update "src/setup_spotify.vala" using a proper username/password
3. Update "src/spotify-source.vala" using a correct LD_LIBRARY_PATH
4. Update "runserver" using a correct LD_LIBRARY_PATH
5. Build the dogvibes server by typing "./compile"


Usage:
Start the server using "./runserver"

Examples:
Use the api scripts in "bashapi" folder to test your server.
